### Main Entry Point

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///c:/Users/shree/OneDrive/Desktop/ExamShield%20v1.0/main.py)
- Add `atexit` handler and `WM_DELETE_WINDOW` handler for graceful cleanup (stop security managers, restore hosts file, unhook keyboard)
- Fix version string inconsistency (title says v1.1 but folder is v1.0)

